data.description: NEW REDUCED PRICE!!! TURNKEY 2 BEDROOM, DEN, 2 FULL BATH, 1782 SQUARE FEET, PRIVATE CULDESAC LOCATION IN THE SOUGHT-AFTER 55+ DEL WEBB-Solera Diamond Valley Community. This home features a large open floor plan. Gorgeous kitchen with upgraded granite countertops and backsplash, large kitchen island, walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances, with pull out storage. Kitchen opens up to the dining room and family room with a custom-built entertainment center. Master bedroom is private with plenty of natural light, large master bathroom, walk in shower, oversized soaking tub and large master closet. Bedroom 2 is located on opposite side of home with a full bath in the hallway. This home also has a nice sized den, currently used as an office, to store your favorite books or use as a hobby room, you decide. 10 Ft Ceilings, Gorgeous tile flooring in all the high traffic areas. Oversized laundry room with a wash sink and plenty of storage cabinets, tankless water heater. Welcoming front porch entry with plenty of room for your favorite outdoor furniture, sip on your favorite drink and enjoy the weather on your quiet street. Low maintenance yards with drought tolerant landscaping, back yard has plenty of space for outdoor entertaining with a California covered concrete patio and walkways on both sides of home, vinyl fencing and fruit trees. The community clubhouse features: a workout center with walking track, library, billiard tables, conference rooms, theater, indoor pool, two outdoor pools, bocce ball courts, tennis courts and pickle ball courts, community has daily, monthly and annual events. Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautiful home, view and submit your offer today.
